escript \u003crelease+treescript@mozilla.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "No bug - Tagging d313e24f18c2d215e0d878a5db83cd7936182263 with DEVEDITION_68_0b1_RELEASE a=release CLOSED TREE DONTBUILD", "files": [".hgtags"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "7e7b48b13b9aec4059b1b6298b9e94b37cc0d44e", "parents": ["5fb7fcd568d6fbc0b205f28d7087a5ad3156456a"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mozilla Releng Treescript \u003crelease+treescript@mozilla.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Automatic version bump CLOSED TREE NO BUG a=release DONTBUILD", "files": ["browser/config/version_display.txt"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "18c20e6dcc0eae461388bae521966c6fedfeec1f", "parents": ["7e7b48b13b9aec4059b1b6298b9e94b37cc0d44e"], "tags": []}], "date": 1557848813, "git_changesets": [null, null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "11270": {"changesets": [{"author": "Andrew Halberstadt \u003cahalberstadt@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1550127 - [ci] Disable release and nightly tasks on ash, r=tomprince\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D30409", "files": ["taskcluster/taskgraph/target_tasks.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "5f723f79b70e9f2fa2fb8ec563686e79267cba8f", "parents": ["96563508f9fed49ddc64469d05c9d3d7be46d547"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Botond Ballo \u003cbotond@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1459260 - Create a MobileViewportManager whenever apz.allow_zooming is set. r=kats\n\nHowever, we continue to only respect a \u003cmeta name=\"viewport\"\u003e tag if\ndom.meta-viewport.enabled is set.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D30988", "files": ["dom/base/Document.cpp", "layout/base/PresShell.cpp", "layout/base/nsLayoutUtils.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "db30d35f71305ef3440f98f1a4e6cb541cca314f", "parents": ["5f723f79b70e9f2fa2fb8ec563686e79267cba8f"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Botond Ballo \u003cbotond@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1459260 - Don't use dom.meta-viewport.enabled in tests that don't need it. r=kats\n\nMany tests only had it enabled because it was required for zooming to work on\ndesktop. This patch revises tests to only use it if they actually use a non-\ndefault meta viewport tag.\n\nThe motivation is to bring test coverage closer to the platform defaults (so\non desktop, tests will run with dom.meta-viewport.enabled=false, and on Android\nwith dom.meta-viewport.enabled=true, matching the production scenarios).\n\nDepends on D30988\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D30989", "files": ["gfx/layers/apz/test/mochitest/apz_test_utils.js", "gfx/layers/apz/test/mochitest/test_group_minimum_scale_size.html", "gfx/layers/apz/test/mochitest/test_group_touchevents-2.html", "gfx/layers/apz/test/mochitest/test_group_touchevents-3.html", "gfx/layers/apz/test/mochitest/test_group_touchevents-4.html", "gfx/layers/apz/test/mochitest/test_group_touchevents.html", "gfx/layers/apz/test/mochitest/test_group_zoom.html"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "ab450513a15615bc3dd1ddf2db999424dc7531d6", "parents": ["db30d35f71305ef3440f98f1a4e6cb541cca314f"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jim Blandy \u003cjimb@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1546727: Make DebuggerFrame_maybeDecrementFrameScriptStepModeCount a method of DebuggerFrame. r=jorendorff\n\nThis function probably predates the existence of the DebuggerFrame class, and\nwas never moved in.\n\nDepends on D28783\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D28784", "files": ["js/src/vm/Debugger.cpp", "js/src/vm/Debugger.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "9224b5e39c2e1e8132929a7be64a71c9531ddd2f", "parents": ["ab450513a15615bc3dd1ddf2db999424dc7531d6"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Matt Woodrow \u003cmwoodrow@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1551061 - Don't reuse a sing