o@crisal.io\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1550377 - Use ManuallyDrop for style structs. r=jwatt\n\nWe destroy them manually, so it's the right thing to do.\n\nThis allows us to not run destructors of any members of nsStyle*, which in turn allows us to:\n\n * Remove the hack that replaced all nsStrings for nsStringReprs.\n * Remove ns{,C}StringRepr (followup)\n * Add members with destructors to the style structs (you see where I'm going :)).\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D30450", "files": ["layout/style/ServoBindings.toml", "layout/style/ServoComputedData.h", "layout/style/ServoComputedDataInlines.h", "servo/components/style/properties/gecko.mako.rs", "servo/ports/geckolib/glue.rs"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "2d0e8bded97ab21731f1577fcf093595aec62c22", "parents": ["db85e84612070c8cd9c75a7cc1b0a50bb5ed2d38"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Matt Woodrow \u003cmwoodrow@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1551389 - Compare line lists as well as lines when deciding if two frames are on the same line. r=mats\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D31152", "files": ["layout/painting/crashtests/1551389-1.html", "layout/painting/crashtests/crashtests.list", "layout/painting/nsCSSRendering.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "9d6897b968f6cd1b1cf525f19a45843907a157e9", "parents": ["2d0e8bded97ab21731f1577fcf093595aec62c22"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Wes Kocher \u003cwkocher@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1550895 - disable some additional frequently failing geckoview wpt tests\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D31158", "files": ["testing/web-platform/meta/css/CSS2/css1/c5525-fltmrgn-000.xht.ini", "testing/web-platform/meta/css/CSS2/css1/c5526-fltclr-000.xht.ini", "testing/web-platform/meta/css/CSS2/text/text-align-bidi-011.xht.ini", "testing/web-platform/meta/css/css-backgrounds/background-atta