 and origin re-escaping from QuotaManager::GetQuotaObject to GetQuotaObjectFromNameAndParameters in TelemetryVFS.cpp; r=janv,asuth a=jcristau\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D33769", "files": ["dom/quota/ActorsParent.cpp", "storage/TelemetryVFS.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "d13ae743074c0570c499c217c1cf9262f74a28c4", "parents": ["2e75aceef9df66dbbfce6ae0f8c1638425d528df"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Eden Chuang \u003cechuang@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1516333 - Part 2: Add LS unit test for uri encoding edge cases; r=janv a=jcristau\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D33617", "files": ["dom/localstorage/test/unit/test_uri_encoding_edge_cases.js", "dom/localstorage/test/unit/xpcshell.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "eacd2f22961f47f00d357814c55d8e707bf5598b", "parents": ["d13ae743074c0570c499c217c1cf9262f74a28c4"], "tags": []}, {"author": "diana.iacos \u003cdiana.iacos@softvision.ro\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1555044 - Update Onboarding's Sync screen text; r=petru a=jcristau l10n=nightly-on-beta\n\nBecause the news strings are unused we need to add them in lint.xml as UnusedResources.\nThe suppress will be removed it in a future patch.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D32979", "files": ["mobile/android/app/lint.xml", "mobile/android/base/locales/en-US/android_strings.dtd", "mobile/android/base/strings.xml.in"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "a08ebd3c9870e93bf8fa57c31791934570529dc0", "parents": ["eacd2f22961f47f00d357814c55d8e707bf5598b"], "tags": []}], "date": 1559934780, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null, null, null, null], "user": "archaeopteryx@coole-files.de"}, "11403": {"changesets": [{"author": "Jon Coppeard \u003cjcoppeard@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1555729 - Improve CallbackObject::CallbackPreserveColor comments to warn about use of Reset(). r=bzbarsky, a=npotb\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D33263", "files": ["dom/bindings/CallbackObject.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "1204f22f153ae799e2eefec9ff13e96bf57f28e8", "parents": ["a08ebd3c9870e93bf8fa57c31791934570529dc0"], "tags": []}, {"author": "D\u00e3o Gottwald \u003cdao@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1463180 - Account for spurious tab switch spinner in opt builds. r=florian, a=test-only\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D33953", "files": ["browser/base/content/test/performance/browser_tabstrip_overflow_underflow.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "81a106c80ef1d04f5de6bc1fbcf59cbe2183604b", "parents": ["1204f22f153ae799e2eefec9ff13e96bf57f28e8"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mike Hommey \u003cmh+mozilla@glandium.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1534578 - Upgrade macosx64 taskcluster tasks to python 3.7. r=ahal, a=release\n\nBug 1501497 deployed python 3.7 on mac workers, while leaving 3.6\naround... except on reimaged workers, which only have 3.7 available.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D31191", "files": ["taskcluster/taskgraph/transforms/job/python_test.py", "taskcluster/taskgraph/transforms/job/run_task.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "230b796e687537a42e81776ccbcb62f93e91609a", "parents": ["81a106c80ef1d04f5de6bc1fbcf59cbe2183604b"], "tags": []}], "date": 1559936792, "git_changesets": [null, null, null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "11404": {"changesets": [{"author": "Paul Bone \u003cpbone@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1556137 - Fix a memory leak by allocating memory statically r=sfink a=test-only\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D33596", "files": ["js/src/builtin/TestingFunctions.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "4b1e3622e260cbfc17e8347e8bcce