W media tests on non-ESR trees. r=gbrown, a=test-only\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D34396", "files": ["taskcluster/ci/test/misc.yml", "taskcluster/ci/test/mochitest.yml"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "259f7d6d4dc9672435bfc90630c6483fb42cf5d8", "parents": ["48542fe2cb4c30618219d0f0c3022b17fec7e467"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mike Hommey \u003cmh@glandium.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1557259 - Fix CPU_ARCH test for libjpeg on mips. r=dmajor, a=jcristau\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D33915", "files": ["media/libjpeg/moz.build"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "cd40c1684a6001500f3a4a261603f1849eb6e9e9", "parents": ["259f7d6d4dc9672435bfc90630c6483fb42cf5d8"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mike Hommey \u003cmh+mozilla@glandium.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1557259 - Don't use clang integrated assembler for jsimd_dspr2.S. r=dmajor, a=jcristau\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D33931", "files": ["media/libjpeg/moz.build"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "5baea46a218f1f526b90cbf2cd00d91ba16adc35", "parents": ["cd40c1684a6001500f3a4a261603f1849eb6e9e9"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Aaron Klotz \u003caklotz@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1558272: Add Windows 10 May 2019 Update to WindowsVersion.h; r=dmajor, a=jcristau\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D34390", "files": ["mfbt/WindowsVersion.h"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "7d0193261d238000fac1ac34025e52d4905a9ad7", "parents": ["5baea46a218f1f526b90cbf2cd00d91ba16adc35"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Philip Chimento \u003cphilip.chimento@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1556210 - Don't use TimeDuration in static initializer. r=jonco, a=jcristau\n\nOn Darwin this would cause a race between two static initializers.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D33416", "files": ["js/src/gc/GC.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "8a4c14d86baa1ab9a8b42cecc0675316de6b9abc", "parents": ["7d0193261d238000fac1ac34025e52d4905a9ad7"], "tags": []}], "date": 1560263867, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null], "user": "ryanvm@gmail.com"}, "11420": {"changesets": [{"author": "Luca Greco \u003clgreco@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1552799 - Hide report action on system and builtin addons. r=mstriemer a=jcristau\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D32625", "files": ["toolkit/mozapps/extensions/content/aboutaddons.js", "toolkit/mozapps/extensions/test/browser/browser_html_abuse_report.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "d512a17f5a554e8b19e21d6ed5055797273d742c", "parents": ["8a4c14d86baa1ab9a8b42cecc0675316de6b9abc"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Dale Harvey \u003cdale@arandomurl.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1552559 - Ensure built in engines are available on startup. r=mikedeboer a=jcristau\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D32320", "files": ["browser/components/search/test/browser/browser_contextmenu.js", "toolkit/components/search/SearchService.jsm", "toolkit/components/search/nsISearchService.idl", "toolkit/components/search/tests/xpcshell/test_selectedEngine.js", "toolkit/components/search/tests/xpcshell/test_webextensions_install.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "52554b40948e17eb3b72a8c742c907fb225a47d7", "parents": ["d512a17f5a554e8b19e21d6ed5055797273d742c"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Dale Harvey \u003cdale@arandomurl.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1556424 - Dont await init() on init() installed engines. r=Standard8 a=jcristau\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D33577", "files": ["toolkit/components/search/SearchService.jsm"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "f2aa60a336fa6dfcec12da4e2e132c34d3973fb4", "parents": ["52554b40948e17eb3b72a8c742c907fb225a47d7"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Botond Ballo \u003cbotond@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1557424 - Re-clamp the scroll offset if the composition bounds changes. r=kats a=jcristau\n\nThis is similar to bug 1551582, but concerns a main-thread change to the\ncomposition bounds rather than the scrollable rect; either can result in\nthe scroll range shrinking and therefore a need to re-clamp the scroll offset.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D34211", "files": ["gfx/layers/apz/src/AsyncPanZoomController.cpp", "gfx/layers/apz/test/gtest/TestTreeManager.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "e94a4d5cd811f4b766af8ba4970452bab29b3f4c", "parents": ["f2aa60a336fa6dfcec12da4e2e132c34d3973fb4"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Chris Pearce \u003ccpearce@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1552145 - Make MediaChangeMonitor by default not try to init decoder until it receives extradata. r=jya a=jcristau\n\nIn bug 1538508 we changed the MediaChangeMonitor to raise an error when we try\nto create a decoder and we don't yet have the H.264 extra data, to maintain the\nassumptions made by OpenH264/WebRTC. This however doesn't play nice with the\nHLS demuxer, which won't always give you extra data after a seek.\n\nSo change the MediaChangeMonitor to by default assume that it should just drop\nframes until it has the extra data it needs to create a decoder. We can flag\nthis mode off in the WebRTC MediaDataDecoder.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D34079", "files": ["dom/media/platforms/PlatformDecoderModule.h", "dom/media/platforms/wrappers/MediaChangeMonitor.cpp", "dom/media/platforms/wrappers/MediaChangeMonitor.h", "media/webrtc/signaling/src/media-conduit/WebrtcMediaDataDecoderCodec.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "eb71282f69a503677fe8a8fecabe38212149fbe9", "parents": ["e94a4d5cd811f4b766af8ba4970452bab29b3f4c"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jan Varga \u003cjan.varga@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1558112 - LSNG: Connection::FlushOp::DoDatastoreWork needs to automatically detach the shadow database on an error; r=asuth a=jcristau\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D34311", "files": ["dom/localstorage/ActorsParent.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "09ffb8ef4a65d03211b31bbe0bf1ea526351a0b7", "parents": ["eb71282f69a503677fe8a8fecabe38212149fbe9"], "tags": []}], "date": 1560267196, "git_changesets": [null, null, null, null, null, null], "user": "nbeleuzu@mozilla.com"}, "11421": {"changesets": [{"author": "Mozilla Releng Treescript \u003crelease+treescript@mozilla.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "No bug - Tagging 6b3dd283de3a5b049d84498c4b1b43de645e1024 with FENNEC_68_0b9_RELEASE a=release CLOSED TREE DONTBUILD", "files": [".hgtags"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "640a6522039241236b6377aa9707485776783883", "parents": ["09ffb8ef4a65d03211b31bbe0bf1ea526351a0b7"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mozilla Releng Treescript \u003crelease+treescript@mozilla.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Automatic version bump CLOSED TREE NO BUG a=release DONTBUILD", "files": ["mobile/android/config/version-files/beta/version_display.txt"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "94e34560b17114ac78ff3080e24447c36d526122", "parents": ["640a6522039241236b6377aa9707485776783883"], "tags": []}], "date": 1560267411, "git_changesets": [null, null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "11422": {"changesets": [{"author": "Mozilla Releng Treescript \u003crelease+treescript@mozilla.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "No bug - Tagging 927b23f07645dd3f1ff4b63d8cf477bec77b9e22 with FIREFOX_68_0b9_RELEASE a=release CLOSED TREE DONTBUILD", "files": [".hgtags"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "bec2621dfad6a4e0318e9bfef4bd074620b7f233", "parents": ["94e34560b17114ac78ff3080e24447c36d526122"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Mozilla Releng Treescript \u003crelease+treescript@mozilla.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Automatic version bump CLOSED TREE NO BUG a=release DONTBUILD", "files": ["browser/config/version_display.txt"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "d5f17085ab28348414be842b0dfd68a0b532266b", "parents": ["bec2621dfad6a4e0318e9bfef4bd074620b7f233"], "tags": []}], "date": 1560267604, "git_changesets": [null, null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "11423": {"changesets": [{"author": "Mozilla Releng Treescript \u003crelease+treescript@mozilla.org\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "No bug - Tagging 927b23f07645dd3f1ff4b63d8cf477bec77b9e22 with DEVEDITION_68_0b9_RELEASE a=release CLOSED TREE DONTBUILD", "files": [".hgtags"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "00fdf7317dfdd5690b902f1f8e2a9ba78146f988", "parents": ["d5f17085ab28348414be842b0dfd68a0b532266b"], "tags": []}], "date": 1560267796, "git_changesets": [null], "user": "ffxbld"}, "11424": {"changesets": [{"author": "Jan Varga \u003cjan.varga@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1546723 - Part 1: Convert WriterOptimizer to a generic reusable class; r=asuth a=jcristau\n\nThis patch creates a new generic class LSWriteOptimizer which can be used with any value type for specific write optimizations either on the parent side or the child side.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D31196", "files": ["dom/localstorage/ActorsParent.cpp", "dom/localstorage/LSWriteOptimizer.cpp", "dom/localstorage/LSWriteOptimizer.h", "dom/localstorage/moz.build"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "3660181b7bca4a5b08bb4b8608ecff2a741a562c", "parents": ["00fdf7317dfdd5690b902f1f8e2a9ba78146f988"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jan Varga \u003cjan.varga@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1546723 - Part 2: Make it more clear that checkpointing also notifies observers; r=asuth a=jcristau\n\nThis patch renames the Checkpoint IPC message to CheckpointAndNotify. Other structures used by checkpointing are renamed too. Datastore methods SetItem/RemoveItem/Clear no longer call NotifyObservers, it's now up to RecvCheckpointAndNotify to call it.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D31197", "files": ["dom/localstorage/ActorsParent.cpp", "dom/localstorage/LSSnapshot.cpp", "dom/localstorage/LSSnapshot.h", "dom/localstorage/PBackgroundLSSnapshot.ipdl"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "4b55e5f016e61ba390b8fc32fdffb9eb08312728", "parents": ["3660181b7bca4a5b08bb4b8608ecff2a741a562c"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jan Varga \u003cjan.varga@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1546723 - Part 3: Change GetSnapshotInitInfo to deal with load info only; r=asuth a=jcristau\n\nThis patch renames GetSnapshotInitInfo to GetSnapshotLoadInfo and removes some arguments that are not directly related to load info.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D31198", "files": ["dom/localstorage/ActorsParent.cpp", "dom/localstorage/PBackgroundLSDatabase.ipdl"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "1521249d7a0721872d481bfa99380e1a6e0962b5", "parents": ["4b55e5f016e61ba390b8fc32fdffb9eb08312728"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jan Varga \u003cjan.varga@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1546723 - Part 4: Use a write optimizer in LSSnapshot; r=asuth a=jcristau\n\nThis patch adds a write optimizer to LSSnapshot. The optimizer is only used when\nthere are no observers for other content processes.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D31199", "files": ["dom/localstorage/ActorsParent.cpp", "dom/localstorage/LSSnapshot.cpp", "dom/localstorage/LSSnapshot.h", "dom/localstorage/PBackgroundLSDatabase.ipdl", "dom/localstorage/PBackgroundLSSnapshot.ipdl", "modules/libpref/init/all.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "ac0e29e198c468325fb2d9bbe4ec9c684f6595c7", "parents": ["1521249d7a0721872d481bfa99380e1a6e0962b5"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jan Varga \u003cjan.varga@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1546723 - Part 5: Generalize code for getting datastores; r=asuth a=jcristau\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D31200", "files": ["dom/localstorage/ActorsParent.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "e23ee28c87d7fc3bd4e37b43a5f4a0b845ddaa38", "parents": ["ac0e29e198c468325fb2d9bbe4ec9c684f6595c7"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jan Varga \u003cjan.varga@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1546723 - Part 6: Mark snapshot as dirty if the hasOtherProcessObservers flag changes; r=asuth a=jcristau\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D31201", "files": ["dom/localstorage/ActorsParent.cpp", "modules/libpref/init/all.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "0a94dff558b1e7fc4ca7779e25c5d1f777574b4d", "parents": ["e23ee28c87d7fc3bd4e37b43a5f4a0b845ddaa38"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jan Varga \u003cjan.varga@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1546723 - Part 7: Fix ordering of items in special cases; r=asuth a=jcristau\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D31202", "files": ["dom/localstorage/ActorsParent.cpp", "dom/localstorage/LSSnapshot.cpp", "dom/localstorage/LSWriteOptimizer.cpp", "dom/localstorage/LSWriteOptimizer.h", "dom/localstorage/test/unit/test_orderingAfterRemoveAdd.js", "dom/localstorage/test/unit/test_snapshotting.js", "dom/localstorage/test/unit/xpcshell.ini"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "ad7c72a799ba407c6117261260593942d3a50f75", "parents": ["0a94dff558b1e7fc4ca7779e25c5d1f777574b4d"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jan Varga \u003cjan.varga@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1546723 - Followup fix: Convert MOZ_DIAGNOSTIC_ASSERT back to MOZ_ASSERT since bug 1541775 hasn't been fixed yet; r=asuth a=jcristau", "files": ["dom/localstorage/ActorsParent.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "2a42b81259f661b8b91573daee509d494a50e1f5", "parents": ["ad7c72a799ba407c6117261260593942d3a50f75"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jan Varga \u003cjan.varga@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1534431 - Part 1: Verify LS request parameters as part of LS request state machine; r=asuth a=jcristau\n\nLS Request parameters are now verified as part of the state machine so an actor\nis always created. Before this patch, we were doing verification prior to actor\ncreation. If the verification failed, we didn't create an actor and content\nwas endlessly waiting for a reply.", "files": ["dom/localstorage/ActorsParent.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "e9a8bcc1834245886d249b4c91467ca2a5984396", "parents": ["2a42b81259f661b8b91573daee509d494a50e1f5"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jan Varga \u003cjan.varga@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1534431 - Part 2: Disallow LS requests with undefined client id; r=asuth a=jcristau\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D33595", "files": ["dom/localstorage/ActorsParent.cpp", "dom/localstorage/LSObject.cpp", "dom/localstorage/test/unit/head.js", "dom/localstorage/test/unit/test_clientValidation.js", "dom/localstorage/test/unit/xpcshell.ini", "dom/quota/test/unit/test_localStorageArchive4upgrade.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "5bc174324f871a279ffa0fb7272bbe397703df36", "parents": ["e9a8bcc1834245886d249b4c91467ca2a5984396"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Jan Varga \u003cjan.varga@gmail.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1557820 - IDB: Add IsShuttingDown check to DatabaseOperationBase::OnProgress; r=asuth a=jcristau\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D34230", "files": ["dom/indexedDB/ActorsParent.cpp"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "2014f3735cc2e37f2a84c214c07d69f1889e3634", "paren