ricator.services.mozilla.com/D34928", "files": ["taskcluster/taskgraph/target_tasks.py"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "c828ca470555167119b752f31be44e0bde92a17c", "parents": ["b72a284cf23d99d22e412f82ae0a0c61c8eb44a0"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Ed Lee \u003cedilee@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1559243 - [AS only] After disabling Pocket section in via about:prefererences, Pocket section can't be re-enabled until restart. r=pdahiya, a=jcristau\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D35294", "files": ["browser/components/newtab/lib/TopStoriesFeed.jsm", "browser/components/newtab/test/unit/lib/TopStoriesFeed.test.js"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "07204fabaf183f107167fa931e828827dc389458", "parents": ["c828ca470555167119b752f31be44e0bde92a17c"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Tim D. Smith \u003ctdsmith@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1558856 - Collect values of MitM-related preferences. r=keeler, a=jcristau\n\nHaving these values in telemetry will let us understand the prevalence of MitM in the wild,\ncount instances of broken AV MitM, and understand how often these values have been manually configured.\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D34741", "files": ["toolkit/components/telemetry/app/TelemetryEnvironment.jsm"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "3d0f2d47703954d9c19b8044e0ebc6e74c8bcfec", "parents": ["07204fabaf183f107167fa931e828827dc389458"], "tags": []}, {"author": "Johann Hofmann \u003cjhofmann@mozilla.com\u003e", "branch": "default", "desc": "Bug 1560192 - Clean up prompt open calls in Prompter.jsm. r=Gijs, a=pascalc\n\nDifferential Revision: https://phabricator.services.mozilla.com/D35371", "files": ["browser/modules/RemotePrompt.jsm", "toolkit/components/prompts/src/Prompter.jsm"], "git_node": null, "git_parents": [null], "node": "4c21940d5185815ccac9f39a7299ac7bec18f9fe", "parents": ["3d0f2d47703954d9c19